All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Actor
    This class stores info about the actor and allows for activities to easily pass actor info between other activities.
    AdminActivity
    Admin Activity allows an admin to perform various task like banning actors and deleting tickets.
    CompanyActivity
    CompanyActivity is used by companies, who have multiple technicians under them, to manage their technicians and track their technicians current ticket or past tickets.
    CreateNewTicketActivity
    CreateNewTicketActivity allows a user to create a new ticket.
    LoginActivity
    LoginActivity allows an existing user to sign in to the app.
    MainActivity
    MainActivity is the landing page when the actor opens the application.
    SignUpActivity
    SignUpActivity takes user input and passes info to the SignUpPresenter in order to create a new actor.
    SignUpModel
    SignUpModel is called by SignUpPresenter and sends a request to the server to create an actor based on the inputs from the presenter.
    SignUpPresenter
    SignUpPresenter handles creating a JSON object to pass to the SignUpModel and passes information back to the SignUpActivity.
    TechActivity
    TechActivity allows technicians to find tickets on the map within a distance of their current location.
    ViewTechTicketActivity
    ViewTechTicketActivity allows a technician to view a user ticket they select on the map.
    ViewTicketsActivity
    ViewTicketsActivity allows a user to view all of their tickets.
    ViewUserTicketActivity
    ViewUserTicketActivity allows a user to view the details of a ticket they select from the ViewTicketsActivity.
